  "originalContent": "<div id=\"readme\" class=\"md\" data-path=\"README.md\"><article class=\"markdown-body entry-content container-lg\" itemprop=\"text\"><p align=\"center\" dir=\"auto\">\n    <a href=\"https://www.halo.run\" rel=\"nofollow\">\n        <img width=\"100\" src=\"https://camo.githubusercontent.com/a7bf43f1b46c1c4d44bf5c727cc38d8350bf1ea5e3b3412fb4bb1b87dce660ed/68747470733a2f2f7777772e68616c6f2e72756e2f6c6f676f\" alt=\"Halo logo\" data-canonical-src=\"https://www.halo.run/logo\" style=\"max-width: 100%;\">\n    </a>\n</p>\n<p align=\"center\" dir=\"auto\"><b>Halo</b> [ˈheɪloʊ]，强大易用的开源建站工具。</p>\n<p align=\"center\" dir=\"auto\">\n<a href=\"https://github.com/halo-dev/halo/releases\"><img alt=\"GitHub release\" src=\"https://camo.githubusercontent.com/00364dee061117e95a7670fb917caf5daad378b9ab6556c14bb2aa99ca367549/68747470733a2f2f696d672e736869656c64732e696f2f6769746875622f72656c656173652f68616c6f2d6465762f68616c6f2e7376673f7374796c653d666c61742d73717561726526696e636c7564655f70726572656c6561736573\" data-canonical-src=\"https://img.shields.io/github/release/halo-dev/halo.svg?style=flat-square&amp;include_prereleases\" style=\"max-width: 100%;\"></a>\n<a href=\"https://hub.docker.com/r/halohub/halo\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"Docker pulls\" src=\"https://camo.githubusercontent.com/7ce8136ecf4310d1c94ac76162bba2c15d28f483b342cbd4c65d0c79605449c4/68747470733a2f2f696d672e736869656c64732e696f2f646f636b65722f70756c6c732f68616c6f6875622f68616c6f3f7374796c653d666c61742d737175617265\" data-canonical-src=\"https://img.shields.io/docker/pulls/halohub/halo?style=flat-square\" style=\"max-width: 100%;\"></a>\n<a href=\"https://github.com/halo-dev/halo/commits\"><img alt=\"GitHub last commit\" src=\"https://camo.githubusercontent.com/f721cd5d1d6ae063fd916ec8f9700176bbfe2f221e8397c899962d3523245649/68747470733a2f2f696d672e736869656c64732e696f2f6769746875622f6c6173742d636f6d6d69742f68616c6f2d6465762f68616c6f2e7376673f7374796c653d666c61742d737175617265\" data-canoni